00:00:09.910 --> 00:00:12.010 align:middle line:84%
>> What does it mean
to be conscious,

00:00:12.010 --> 00:00:15.550 align:middle line:84%
to be aware of and respond
to one's surroundings,

00:00:15.550 --> 00:00:19.090 align:middle line:84%
a behavior that implies
the existence of a brain

00:00:19.090 --> 00:00:21.280 align:middle line:90%
and a nervous system?

00:00:21.280 --> 00:00:26.142 align:middle line:10%
I'm your host, Bruce Lipton, for
this series on Inner Evolution.

00:00:26.142 --> 00:00:28.622 align:middle line:90%
